Question
9:
Bank Loan EMI Calculator System
Scenario
A banking system needs a function to calculate EMI (Equated Monthly Installment) based on:
Principal amount
Annual interest rate
Loan tenure (in years)
Question
Write an R function to calculate EMI.
Answer (R Program)
calculate_emi <- function(principal, rate, years){
monthly_rate <- rate / (12 * 100)
months <- years * 12
emi <- (principal * monthly_rate * (1 + monthly_rate)^months) /
((1 + monthly_rate)^months - 1)
 
return(round(emi, 2))
}
calculate_emi(500000, 7.5, 10)
 
