Question
11:
Online Shopping Order Processing System
Scenario
An e-commerce platform calculates final order amount based on:
Total cart value
Discount (10% if cart ≥ ₹3000)
Delivery fee (₹0 if cart ≥ ₹5000, else ₹100)
Question
Write an R function to compute final payable amount.
Answer
order_total <- function(cart_value){
if(cart_value >= 3000){
discount <- cart_value * 0.10
} else {
discount <- 0
}
if(cart_value >= 5000){
delivery <- 0
} else {
delivery <- 100
}
final_amount <- cart_value - discount + delivery
return(final_amount)
}
order_total(4200)
 
