15:
Employee Payroll Processing System
Scenario
A payroll system calculates:
HRA = 20% of basic
DA = 10% of basic
Tax = 12% of gross salary
Question
Write an R function to calculate net salary.
Answer
payroll <- function(basic){
hra <- basic * 0.20
da <- basic * 0.10
gross <- basic + hra + da
tax <- gross * 0.12
net <- gross - tax
return(net)
}
